      <title>随着美国国债收益率攀升，日元感受到压力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-feels-heat-us-treasury-yields-climb-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周二表现试探，未能从美国国债收益率上升中获得有意义的提振，但这对日元造成压力，日元在数十年低点附近徘徊，并让交易员对任何干预迹象保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-feels-heat-us-treasury-yields-climb-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:30:17 GMT</pubDate>
